text.tspan: Time spent on activities on an average day, by sex, Sweden, 2010
Average minutes spent on a particular activity, by sex, aged 20-84 years, on an average day in Sweden. Estimates
take a weighted average of minutes spent on a particular activity on weekdays and on the weekend.
